info.name: Impractical Google V01
info.description: A theme I made purely to annoy people who wanted to use my laptop when I was gone. A friend asked me to upload it. Do not use it if you want to be able to see search results properly.
info.additionalInfo: It was designed to look horrible and reduce functionality so please don't spam me with complaints. I have told you that it's not suitable for normal use so if you download it expecting it to be super usable it's not my fault.
